data.description: Come enjoy this beautiful home situated in the sought-after neighborhood of Cresthaven. Located just 10 minutes from the beach, this home invites you to embrace the coastal lifestyle. It boasts natural night and has stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, and tile floors throughout. The large window in the living space brings in an airy ambiance throughout the home. The bedrooms are spacious and the master has a large walk-in closet. Backyard is fenced and spacious, ready to entertain your guests. Extra storage facility attached to the back of the home for your convenience. This home would make a perfect family residence or investment property. Located perfectly so that you are minutes away from great restaurants, Publix, shopping center, etc.
